import React from 'react';
import Theme from './components/Theme'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import NavItems from './components/NavItems'
import NavItem from './components/NavItem'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import Play from './components/Play'
import Create from './components/Create'
import Create2 from './components/Create2'
import Home from './components/Home'


class App extends React.Component {
	render() {
	return(
		<Router>
		    <Theme>
		    	<Navbar top>
		    		<NavItems justify='center'>	    			
		    			<NavItem ref='b1' onClick={()=>{ console.log('hey') } }><Link to='/'>HOME</Link></NavItem>
			    		<NavItem><Link to='/create'>CREATE</Link></NavItem>
			    		<NavItem><Link to='/play'>PLAY</Link></NavItem>
		    		</NavItems>
		    	</Navbar>



		        <Switch>
		          <Route path="/create">
		            <Create />
		          </Route>
		          <Route path="/play">
		            <Play />
		          </Route>
		          <Route path="/create2">
		            <Create2 />
		          </Route>		          
		          <Route path="/">
		            <Home />
		          </Route>
		        </Switch>	    

		    </Theme>
		</Router>
	);
	}
}

export default App;
